    • ContactModel

      public ContactModel(int authorId, String senderEmail, String messageText, String senderName)
      Constructor without messageId and messageDate. Useful when creating a new message before it is saved (and ID/date assigned).
      Parameters:
      authorId - ID of the author who will receive the message
      senderEmail - Email of the sender
      messageText - Text content of the message
      senderName - Name of the sender

    • ContactModel

      public ContactModel(int messageId, String senderEmail, String messageText, String senderName, LocalDateTime messageDate)
      Full constructor including messageId and messageDate. Useful when loading an existing message from the database.
      Parameters:
      messageId - Unique message ID
      senderEmail - Email of the sender
      messageText - Text content of the message
      senderName - Name of the sender
      messageDate - Date and time the message was sent
